{"tid":1024332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府政策全面反映關愛精神","createTime":"2019-02-16T12:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T16:54:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bcca5464aa4f45958dfa709cb611c117b64de5c2","tid":1024332,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗出席活動致辭時表示，關愛精神在政府政策上全面反映，他指，政府每100元當中，分別有19.7元投放在福利、20.8元在教育和17.5元分配在醫療，這3項都是政府開支最大的項目。他又說，政府會繼續投放資源，建立關愛共融的平等社會。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗列出多項政府在未來數月即將推行的政策，包括電梯優化計劃、持續進修基金金額增加和最低工資時薪調高3元等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1443188-20190216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1443188-20190216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7Lx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=36a29e40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1443188-20190216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=458447f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1443188-20190216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5a4b7833a44f9f16d4ac616d9b0a29196324674f","tid":1024332,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"褔利, 新移民落地老綜<br />\n教育, 國民教育, 普教中<br />\n醫療, 10個有8個r字頭排隊"},{"pid":"f4a8f08c76c2757822ef6e6e37010790c2d66149","tid":1024332,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa154704adb2d231c34214a49a130210a21bee4f","tid":1024332,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"都係攞撚晒去貼大陸狗架啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9c89c6a9f6fe753d665ffd217104f81b44c22a43","tid":1024332,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"4成同班人貪左佢？"},{"pid":"69a27ced7231be7f398cf3f4ee18a8db16b8a4f6","tid":1024332,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike"